<li>Explore the <a href="https://www.exploratorium.edu/explore" target="_blank">
activities by subjects</a> and <br> watch 
    <a href="https://www.exploratorium.edu/video" target="_blank">fun videos</a> 
    to learn science</li> 

<li>Covers the full spectrum of science, e.g., biology, physics, chemistry, 
earth science and astronomy</li>
<li>Adults can have fun learning here too!</li>